sourcesContent: import React from "react"; import { MDBTable, MDBTableHead, MDBTableBody, MDBBtn } from "mdbreact"; const DataTable = ({ data, toggleModal }) => ( Hash Value Description Actions {data.map((item) => ( {item.hash_value} {item.description} /{" "} toggleModal("edit", item)}> Edit toggleModal("delete", item)}> Delete ))} ); export default DataTable;
